Alice in La-La Land 🌬️🌿✨

Before my 28th birthday, and on the way towards celebrating my 10th year in Los Angeles, I had the absolute pleasure of collaborating with star-catcher @likes.this for this dreamy shoot. A couple hours spent hiking, playing in the woods & having good conversation reminds me of how grateful I am to claim this life as both a passion and a career. Thank you so much again, Kyle I am and was honored to be in front of your lens!

Also in collaboration, @makeupp_by_natalee on the beautiful & natural makeup 💄
And my lovely friend @mariespieldenner on styling 🎀

How special these moments in time are & will forever be, to me.
